---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | A Thinking Workspace"
  description="About Shailesh Rawat and this thinking workspace: systems writing, reflective notes, and practical AI documentation."
  image="/my-self-portrait.png"
>
  <h1>About This Space</h1>
  <p>
    This website is an experiment in public thinking. It's a place to develop ideas, connect concepts, and document my explorations into technology, systems, and language.
  </p>
  <p>
    The work moves through three modes: technical systems that explain how things function, reflective sentences that slow the thinking down, and poetic sticky notes that keep the raw signal alive.
  </p>
  <p>
    The core thesis is that the process of thinking is as valuable as the finished product. I'm sharing notes, fragments, and long-form essays, in the hope to create a more honest and dynamic representation of my work. The content here is intentionally fluid and subject to change as my understanding evolves.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you're looking for a focused view of my documentation and enablement work, the portfolio lives here: <a class="about-portfolio-link" href="/portfolio/">/portfolio</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="about-social-intro">You can find me here:</p>
  <div class="about-social-links">
    <a href="mailto:shailesh.rawat1403@gmail.com" class="about-social-link" aria-label="Email Shailesh Rawat">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
        <path d="M4 6h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Zm0 2 8 5 8-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
      <span>Email</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shailesh-rawat" class="about-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Shailesh Rawat on LinkedIn">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
        <path d="M4 9h4v11H4V9Zm2-5a2 2 0 1 1 0 4 2 2 0 0 1 0-4Zm6 5h4v2.2c.6-1.2 2.1-2.4 4.3-2.4 4.6 0 5.4 3 5.4 6.9V20h-4v-6.3c0-1.5 0-3.4-2.1-3.4-2.1 0-2.4 1.6-2.4 3.3V20h-4V9Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
      <span>LinkedIn</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com/ShaileshRawat1403" class="about-social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Shailesh Rawat on GitHub">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
        <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-3.2 19.5c.5.1.7-.2.7-.5v-1.8c-2.8.6-3.4-1.3-3.4-1.3-.4-1-.9-1.3-.9-1.3-.8-.5.1-.5.1-.5.9.1 1.4.9 1.4.9.8 1.4 2.2 1 2.7.8.1-.6.3-1 .6-1.2-2.2-.2-4.5-1.1-4.5-4.9 0-1.1.4-2 1-2.7-.1-.2-.4-1.2.1-2.5 0 0 .8-.3 2.7 1a9.5 9.5 0 0 1 4.9 0c1.9-1.3 2.7-1 2.7-1 .5 1.3.2 2.3.1 2.5.6.7 1 1.6 1 2.7 0 3.8-2.3 4.7-4.5 4.9.3.3.7.8.7 1.7v2.5c0 .3.2.6.7.5A10 10 0 0 0 12 2Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
      <span>GitHub</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-social-intro {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .about-social-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-social-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    background-color: var(--color-blockquote-bg);
  }
  .about-social-link svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }
  .about-social-link:hover {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 40%, var(--color-border));
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }
  .about-portfolio-link {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .about-portfolio-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
